# Testing CRUD functionality for Pokemon-Teams API

@base=http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1


### All Pokedex entries
GET {{base}}/pokedex/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json


### Sprites for charizard (all forms)
GET {{base}}/sprite/6 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json


### All teams
GET {{base}}/team HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json


### Get a team
GET {{base}}/team/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json


